            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-shadow-chunky text-cream">Machine Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-cream">AI models, predictions, and intelligent systems that actually make sense.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Data, Analytics & Integration -->
        <div class="box-wonky bg-dark p-6">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-neon-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-shadow-chunky text-cream">Data, Analytics & Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-cream">Data warehouses, pipelines, and dashboards that reveal the truth.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Growth Marketing -->
        <div class="box-brutal bg-dark p-6 rotate-slight">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-neon-purple" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-shadow-chunky text-cream">Growth Marketing</h3>
          <p class="text-cream">Finding what it takes to move the dial in your business, improve performance or grow the pie.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Strategy -->
        <div class="box-wonky bg-dark p-6">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-neon-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 20l-5.447-2.724A1 1 0 013 16.382V5.618a1 1 0 011.447-.894L9 7m0 13l6-3m-6 3V7m6 10l4.553 2.276A1 1 0 0021 18.382V7.618a1 1 0 00-.553-.894L15 4m0 13V4m0 0L9 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-shadow-chunky text-cream">Strategy</h3>
