      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-neon-yellow pattern-waves px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-12 text-shadow-thick rotate-slight inline-block text-dark">
        Meet the Loon
      </h2>

      <div class="box-brutal bg-dark p-8 md:p-12">
        <p class="text-2xl mb-6 leading-relaxed text-cream">
          Hey there, I'm <span class="font-bold bg-neon-pink text-cream px-2 py-1 border-2 border-cream">Grayson Campbell</span> - the chief loon behind this "massive" operation.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed text-cream">
          I operate at the intersection of Product, Engineering, and Marketing - with a rare ability to shift from C-level strategy to hands-on coding at a moment's notice. Currently building AI-first workflows and high-growth distribution networks as Head of Digital & Growth at <a href="https://www.papercut.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline font-bold hover:bg-neon-pink hover:text-cream px-1 transition-colors">PaperCut</a>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl mb-6 leading-relaxed text-cream">
          I have a disturbing ability with stitching things together that probably shouldn't work - making tools talk to each other in ways they weren't designed for, automating workflows people said were "too complex," and building growth marketing tools that give small teams superpowers.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl mb-8 leading-relaxed text-cream">
          If someone tells me "that's not how it's supposed to work," I take it as a challenge. The tools I build are for people who want to grow their business and do things differently, who refuse to put things in the too hard basket. They can and will find a way to make things happen. Love you folks.
        </p>

        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/graysoncampbell/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="box-brutal bg-electric-blue text-cream px-8 py-4 text-xl font-bold inline-flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-neon-cyan pattern-grid px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-12 text-shadow-thick text-dark">
        Get in Touch
      </h2>

      <div class="box-brutal bg-cream p-8 md:p-12">
        <form id="contact-form" method="post" name="contact">
          <div id="form-message" class="mb-4 p-4 rounded-md hidden"></div>

          <p class="my-3">
            <label class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Your Name:</label>
          </p>
          <p class="my-3">
            <input
              type="text"
              name="name"
              required
              class="p-2 border-solid border-5 border-dark rounded-md shadow-xl text-xl w-full"
            />
          </p>

          <p class="my-3">
            <label class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Your Email:</label>
          </p>
          <p class="my-3">
            <input
              type="email"
              name="email"
              required
              class="p-2 border-solid border-5 border-dark rounded-md shadow-xl text-xl w-full"
            />
          </p>

          <p class="my-3">
            <label class="text-xl font-bold text-dark">Message:</label>
          </p>
          <p class="mb-0">
            <textarea
              name="message"
              rows="5"
              required
              class="p-2 border-solid border-5 border-dark rounded-md shadow-xl text-xl w-full resize-none"
            ></textarea>
          </p>

          <p class="mt-0">
            <button
              type="submit"
              id="submit-button"
              class="underline underline-offset-2 mt-6 text-3xl font-bold text-dark hover:text-neon-pink transition-colors"
            >
              Send
            </button>
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-12 bg-charcoal px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <img src="/images/loonshoot-logo.png" alt="Loonshoot Logo" class="h-10 w-auto" />
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-yellow">loonshoot.</h2>
      </div>

      <p class="text-cream font-mono mb-2">Copyright Â© Loon Shoot PTY LTD 2025</p>
      <p class="text-cream font-mono text-sm mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-neon-pink" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path>
        </svg>
        from Geelong, Australia
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-neon-pink font-mono text-lg font-bold">
          Building the impossible. Making it happen. ðŸš€
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('contact-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const submitButton = document.getElementById('submit-button') as HTMLButtonElement;
  const formMessage = document.getElementById('form-message') as HTMLDivElement;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();

    // Disable submit button
    submitButton.disabled = true;
    submitButton.textContent = 'Sending...';

    try {
      const formData = new FormData(form);
      const response = await fetch('/api/contact', {
        method: 'POST',
        body: formData,
      });

      const data = await response.json();

      if (response.ok) {
        // Success
        formMessage.textContent = 'Thanks! Your message has been sent successfully.';
        formMessage.className = 'mb-4 p-4 rounded-md bg-neon-green text-dark font-bold';
        form.reset();
      } else {
        // Error
        formMessage.textContent = data.error || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.';
        formMessage.className = 'mb-4 p-4 rounded-md bg-neon-pink text-cream font-bold';
      }
    } catch (error) {
      formMessage.textContent = 'Failed to send message. Please try again later.';
      formMessage.className = 'mb-4 p-4 rounded-md bg-neon-pink text-cream font-bold';
    } finally {
      // Re-enable submit button
      submitButton.disabled = false;
      submitButton.textContent = 'Send';
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
</style>
